## Test Bench

**Objectives:** improve skills in Pytest, CI/CD, HIL, and testing for embedded systems

### Documentation

- [CI/CD](docs/cicd.md)
- [Docker Containerization](docs/docker.md)
- [Python Test Framework](docs/framework.md)
- [Daily Progress](docs/daily.md)

### Instructions

1. Build and run the Docker container. 

Notes:
- `-t`: shows container's output in the host terminal
- `-rm`: automatically delete the container when it is done running
- After making changes, build the container before running it

```
docker build -t test-bench .
docker run --rm test-bench
```